s to discover.\n\n**In this demo, play all 5 levels of World 1 including the Final Dungeon.**\n\n**How To Play:**\n\n  - Movement - Left & Right Thumbsticks\n  - Jump - A Button or Click Right Thumbstick\n  - Run - Click Left Thumbstick\n  - Ground Smash - While in Air (Press either Trigger)", "short_description": "RUN, JUMP, PUNCH & SMASH your way through 40+ levels and dungeons in this retro-themed VR platformer & obstacle course game. Filled with tough challenges, inventive obstacles, treasures to collect and secrets to discover."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.ninjaplayground.com/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ludas Vision", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.ninjaplayground.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8551036228291395"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1173921877052193"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1173921877052193"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1727825280, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1173921877052193"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8547181538676864", "version": "8.1"}, "id": "956994796473251", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_ke